A MAN has been arrested in connection with the alleged rape of a teenager. Man arrested over cycle path rape A MAN has been arrested in connection with the alleged rape of a teenager.The 29 year-old was arrested after the 18-year-old victim was allegedly attacked on a cycle path between Johnstone and Linwood in Renfrewshire.It happened at around 2.15pm on Thursday.The man is expected to appear at Paisley Sheriff Court tomorrow.Police confirmed a report will be sent to the procurator fiscal.A spokeswoman said: &quot;A 29 year-old man has been arrested in connection with the incident.&quot;